  "label": "Rafter Bedroom",
  "description": "Rafter Bedroom forms the loft’s enclosed sleeping room beneath soot-dark rafters, its ceiling pitched so low that the beams dominate the space. A narrow cot-platform and a built-in chest occupy the wall opposite a slit window, whose deep embrasure is scored with measurement marks and stained by wax and lamp soot. The plastered lath walls bear repairs in mismatched limewash, and iron strap-bracing remains exposed where the ancient masonry shifts under the bastion load. The air retains lime dust and smoke, consistent with Cindervale’s regulated, record-bound frontier life.",
